{"tid":2515583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯：美英兩國將繼續合作應對香港、新疆問題","createTime":"2021-05-04T05:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T06:49:38.000Z","uid":227801,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7beabe5c900285889cbce48102df939f9a71e235","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"[url]https://new<del><a href=\"http://s.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=90d13777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId</a></del>=433502[/url]<br />\n【Now新聞台】在倫敦出席七國集團外長會議的美國國務卿布林肯與英國外相藍韜文，舉行雙邊會談，指西方無意遏制中國，但一定會捍衛以國際規則為基礎的秩序，並認為中國必須履行，包括對香港在內的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿布林肯與英國外相藍韜文會面，布林肯會後指，西方國家無意遏制中國。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯：「我們無意嘗試圍堵或遏制中國，我們要做的是捍衛，以國際規則為基礎的秩序，我們過去數十年為此投入不少心力。」<br />\n<br />\n布林肯表示，若中國或其他國家試圖挑戰或破壞，以國際規則為基礎的秩序，美國等國家將會挺身而出捍衛秩序。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯又指出，美英兩國將繼續合作，應對新疆及香港問題，以及中國及全球各地傳媒自由被打壓。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯提到，香港的民主支持者及政治人物遭到打壓，顯示中國違反國際承諾。藍韜文亦表示，會要求北京履行對香港的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文：「我們都同意有需要捍衛我們的價值觀，要求北京履行所作承諾，無論是《中英聯合聲明》、對香港的承諾，或其他更廣泛承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n至於朝鮮半島核問題，布林肯說希望平壤把握機會，以外交途徑打破僵局，美國不只會觀察北韓的言論，亦會觀察對方的實際作為。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯又指出，美國希望與俄羅斯維持比較穩定的關係，但指這視乎俄羅斯的行為，若對方肆意妄為，美國將作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n為期三天的七國集團外長會議，會討論多項議題，並且為下月的峰會作準備。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文指，英國將藉擔任輪任主席國的機會，尋求民主社會團結一致，應對共同挑戰及威脅。"},{"pid":"9c1e399ba4f491137dbe662d5ceab360032e6ea7","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3d127cbfd26f8053d78e90bd91b79a913a92c1","tid":2515583,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"american great again!<br />\ngod save the queen!"},{"pid":"0ef79109d97097b5b9ca9b7968e65a1c4c2401ce","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ca417170ffe369be29ed5ad43e87c82543de84","tid":2515583,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"又唔係送槍畀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dea3987bba67f886d717cbd200df0c81d40309","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed813def9bf92d1318da8e13bd76b0b123a6bcd4","tid":2515583,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"咁英國制裁左777未？"},{"pid":"d8e9eebeb48cce47eab475d37ca71211bbd1a0de","tid":2515583,"uid":53844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"即係廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7024408ecd166937ba54470c35fe1eaaf08755","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104c22cdbab6dbf2cd9aaeab687aeaec92e51e6b","tid":2515583,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}